<text><body>
<pb n="0680b" xml:id="T19.1011.0680b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0680b01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0680b02" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1011 [Nos. 1009, 1012-1018]</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0680b03" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0680005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本</note>佛說無量門微密持經<note n="0680006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一名…智〕十字－【三】</note><note n="0680006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一名…智〕十字－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app cb:word-count="10" n="0680006"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">一名成道降魔得一切智</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0680b04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0680b05" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">吳<note n="0680007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">月支＝月氏【宋】，月氏國【元】【明】</note><note n="0680007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月支＝月氏【宋】，＝月氏國【元】【明】</note><app n="0680007"><lem wit="【大】">月支</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">月氏</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">月氏國</rdg></app>優婆塞支謙譯</byline>
<lb n="0680b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0680b0601">聞如是。一時佛遊於維耶離國大樹精舍。佛
<lb n="0680b07" ed="T"/>告賢者大目揵連。汝行請<note n="0680008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（諸）＋遊【三】</note><note n="0680008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（諸）＋遊【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680008"><lem wit="【大】">遊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">諸遊</rdg></app>三千大千世界
<lb n="0680b08" ed="T"/>比丘。為弟子行及菩薩行者使會。目連受教
<lb n="0680b09" ed="T"/>步須彌頂。以道神力周遍佛界聲告使知。應
<lb n="0680b10" ed="T"/>時精舍有四十萬比丘會。復現神足令是天
<lb n="0680b11" ed="T"/>下<note n="0680009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">猗＝倚【三】＊</note><note n="0680009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">猗＝倚【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0680009"><lem wit="【大】">猗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">倚</rdg></app>行比丘。悉會精舍稽首畢一面住。佛復
<lb n="0680b12" ed="T"/>告慧見菩薩敬首菩薩。除憂菩薩虞界菩薩。
<lb n="0680b13" ed="T"/>去蓋菩薩<note n="0680010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">闚＝𨶳【宋】</note><app n="0680010"><lem wit="【大】">闚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">𨶳</rdg></app>音菩薩。殆棄菩薩眾<note n="0680011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">首＝手【三】</note><note n="0680011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">首＝手【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680011"><lem wit="【大】">首</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">手</rdg></app>菩薩。
<lb n="0680b14" ed="T"/>辯<note n="0680012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">音＝立【三】</note><note n="0680012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">音＝立【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680012"><lem wit="【大】">音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">立</rdg></app>菩薩慈氏菩薩。汝等行請十方無央數
<lb n="0680b15" ed="T"/>佛國諸一生補處。無所從生法忍。及不退轉
<lb n="0680b16" ed="T"/>信解菩薩悉令會此。即皆受教而為感應。<note n="0680013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（應）＋時【三】</note><note n="0680013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（應）＋時【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680013"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">應時</rdg></app>
<lb n="0680b17" ed="T"/>有八百億一生補處菩薩。三百億得無所從
<lb n="0680b18" ed="T"/>生法忍菩薩。百億不退轉菩薩。六百億信解
<lb n="0680b19" ed="T"/>菩薩。皆乘佛<note n="0680014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔聖〕－【三】</note><note n="0680014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔聖〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680014"><lem wit="【大】">聖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>旨神足來會。</p>
<lb n="0680b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0680b2001">賢者舍利弗見大眾會。心念當問如來妙行。
<lb n="0680b21" ed="T"/>演現其要令諸菩薩。一切望畢得無礙辯。<note n="0680015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遠＝逮【三】</note><note n="0680015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遠＝逮【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680015"><lem wit="【大】">遠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">逮</rdg></app>
<lb n="0680b22" ed="T"/>聞十方無數剎土諸佛說法念不中忘。至於
<lb n="0680b23" ed="T"/>無上正真之道為最正覺。疾使菩薩得四清
<lb n="0680b24" ed="T"/>淨。何等為四。一曰人淨。二曰法淨。三曰慧
<lb n="0680b25" ed="T"/>淨。四曰佛國嚴淨。亦疾使菩薩得四願悅。何
<lb n="0680b26" ed="T"/>等為四。一曰身和悅。二曰言和悅。三曰意和
<lb n="0680b27" ed="T"/>悅。四曰滅和悅。已得四願悅便入四持門。何
<lb n="0680b28" ed="T"/>等為四。一曰如文行入持門。二曰內深忍入
<lb n="0680b29" ed="T"/>持門。三曰解人根<note n="0680016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">德＝得【三】</note><note n="0680016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">德＝得【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680016"><lem wit="【大】">德</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">得</rdg></app>入持門。四曰知行報善
<pb n="0680c" xml:id="T19.1011.0680c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0680c01" ed="T"/>入持門。舍利弗思念。是菩薩清淨無量慧地
<lb n="0680c02" ed="T"/>欲令佛說。</p>
<lb n="0680c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0680c0301">於是佛語<note n="0680017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔賢者〕－【三】</note><note n="0680017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔賢者〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680017"><lem wit="【大】">賢者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>舍利弗。讚言善哉意至。欲使
<lb n="0680c04" ed="T"/>諸菩薩疾成持行。若舍利弗菩薩行此持要
<lb n="0680c05" ed="T"/>句者。疾入無量之門得微密持。謂是無為無
<lb n="0680c06" ed="T"/>向如正意解。為應為滅內明順道為履上迹。
<lb n="0680c07" ed="T"/>如微妙行不動寂靜。無<note n="0680018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">量＝意【三】</note><note n="0680018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">量＝意【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680018"><lem wit="【大】">量</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">意</rdg></app>無<note n="0680019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">上＝生【三】</note><note n="0680019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上＝生【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680019"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">生</rdg></app>微密無垢。
<lb n="0680c08" ed="T"/>清淨自然惟無。惟無所著<note n="0680020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">明光＝光明【三】</note><note n="0680020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">明光＝光明【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680020"><lem wit="【大】">明光</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">光明</rdg></app>悅懌。果而大
<lb n="0680c09" ed="T"/>勇為美譽。動無動以正動近道。因能善<note n="0680021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">與＝譽【三】</note><note n="0680021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">與＝譽【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680021"><lem wit="【大】">與</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">譽</rdg></app>遊
<lb n="0680c10" ed="T"/>無罣礙入諸法門。強而有勢光大照。遠解等
<lb n="0680c11" ed="T"/>意無不入不斷持實。如是舍利弗行持菩薩
<lb n="0680c12" ed="T"/>非有數也。行無數法為不以知故。諸法斷覺
<lb n="0680c13" ed="T"/>而不作不見合法離。不見起不見滅。不有去
<lb n="0680c14" ed="T"/>來現在之<note n="0680022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">智＝知【三】</note><note n="0680022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智＝知【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680022"><lem wit="【大】">智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">知</rdg></app>。亦不知法。已成未成隨佛念行
<lb n="0680c15" ed="T"/>不念相。亦不好<note n="0680023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（亦）＋不【三】</note><note n="0680023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（亦）＋不【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680023"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">亦不</rdg></app>種<note n="0680024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">姓＝性【明】</note><app n="0680024"><lem wit="【大】">姓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">性</rdg></app>。不群從不方土。不
<lb n="0680c16" ed="T"/>勞盡不<note n="0680025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＝已【三】</note><note n="0680025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680025"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">已</rdg></app>知無。不知不人淨不<note n="0680026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法說＝說法【三】</note><note n="0680026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法說＝說法【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680026"><lem wit="【大】">法說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">說法</rdg></app>。不我
<lb n="0680c17" ed="T"/>利不彼利。不法<note n="0680027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（不）＋律【三】</note><note n="0680027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（不）＋律【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680027"><lem wit="【大】">律</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">不律</rdg></app>不行不除。不念身不念
<lb n="0680c18" ed="T"/>人。於一切法行無受者名為念佛。為一切法
<lb n="0680c19" ed="T"/>之正歸也。為是無畏持義之藏。妙願已滿上
<lb n="0680c20" ed="T"/>道已備。調靜諸定一切德本。不由彼致自從
<lb n="0680c21" ed="T"/>法生。種<note n="0680028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">姓＝性【三】</note><note n="0680028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姓＝性【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680028"><lem wit="【大】">姓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">性</rdg></app>相好其行自然。無邪行無斷行。
<lb n="0680c22" ed="T"/>是為菩薩能學無量門微密之持。為不退轉
<lb n="0680c23" ed="T"/>於無上正真之道。所以者何是從眾生之行。
<lb n="0680c24" ed="T"/>而致無量得行之持。於是佛說偈言。</p>
<lb n="0680c25" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0680c2501"><l>法空無望得</l><l>為道莫自恣</l>
<lb n="0680c26" ed="T"/><l>奉經而不亂</l><l><note n="0680029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">則是＝是則【三】</note><note n="0680029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則是＝是則【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0680029"><lem wit="【大】">則是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">是則</rdg></app>疾得持</l>
<lb n="0680c27" ed="T"/><l>是經義為妙</l><l>持無極常念</l>
<lb n="0680c28" ed="T"/><l>學<note n="0680030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">聞斯＝文斯【宋】，聞思【元】【明】</note><note n="0680030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聞斯＝文斯【宋】，＝聞思【元】【明】</note><app n="0680030"><lem wit="【大】">聞斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">文斯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">聞思</rdg></app>慧者</l><l>可得成道行</l>
<lb n="0680c29" ed="T"/><l>菩薩得此持</l><l>常行精進者</l>
<pb n="0681a" xml:id="T19.1011.0681a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0681a01" ed="T"/><l>十方彼諸佛</l><l>說法輒得聞</l>
<lb n="0681a02" ed="T"/><l>一切能受持</l><l>執義正不忘</l>
<lb n="0681a03" ed="T"/><l>意解如日明</l><l>自恣微妙行</l>
<lb n="0681a04" ed="T"/><l>至於無上法</l><l>弘大持之門</l>
<lb n="0681a05" ed="T"/><l>一切是得向</l><l>為能擁護經</l>
<lb n="0681a06" ed="T"/><l>正使一切人</l><l>盡劫共難<note n="0681001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">聞＝問【宋】【元】</note><app n="0681001"><lem wit="【大】">聞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">問</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0681a07" ed="T"/><l>悉能解諸結</l><l>其智不可極</l>
<lb n="0681a08" ed="T"/><l>是<note n="0681002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">坐＝生【三】</note><note n="0681002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坐＝生【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681002"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">生</rdg></app>上道<note n="0681003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">者＝署【三】</note><note n="0681003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者＝署【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681003"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">署</rdg></app></l><l>得為法王子</l>
<lb n="0681a09" ed="T"/><l>常厚護持法</l><l>內性好斯經</l>
<lb n="0681a10" ed="T"/><l>菩薩所<note n="0681004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">貴＝敬【三】</note><note n="0681004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">貴＝敬【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681004"><lem wit="【大】">貴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">敬</rdg></app>重</l><l>十方佛亦愛</l>
<lb n="0681a11" ed="T"/><l>名譽蓋於世</l><l>行此為無量</l>
<lb n="0681a12" ed="T"/><l>八十億諸佛</l><l>終時悉得見</l>
<lb n="0681a13" ed="T"/><l>一切皆授手</l><l>接行此持者</l>
<lb n="0681a14" ed="T"/><l>若於往千劫</l><l>而為不善行</l>
<lb n="0681a15" ed="T"/><l>一<note n="0681005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">月＝日【三】</note><note n="0681005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月＝日【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681005"><lem wit="【大】">月</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">日</rdg></app>可以除</l><l>但當守此經</l>
<lb n="0681a16" ed="T"/><l>菩薩所興福</l><l>億劫來積聚</l>
<lb n="0681a17" ed="T"/><l>善誦是持者</l><l>一日可與等</l>
<lb n="0681a18" ed="T"/><l>念意<note n="0681006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">如＝而【三】</note><note n="0681006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如＝而【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681006"><lem wit="【大】">如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">而</rdg></app>強意</l><l>思惟此上持</l>
<lb n="0681a19" ed="T"/><l>向行眾德本</l><l>必成至覺道</l>
<lb n="0681a20" ed="T"/><l>假使三界人</l><l>一切悉為魔</l>
<lb n="0681a21" ed="T"/><l>不能中得害</l><l>唯行<note n="0681007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">是＝此【三】</note><note n="0681007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是＝此【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681007"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">此</rdg></app>經者</l>
<lb n="0681a22" ed="T"/><l>是說幻如諦</l><l>為極法之要</l>
<lb n="0681a23" ed="T"/><l>諸佛自此出</l><l>道意所由生</l>
<lb n="0681a24" ed="T"/><l>昔吾學道時</l><l>得決於<note n="0681008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">錠＝定【三】</note><note n="0681008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">錠＝定【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681008"><lem wit="【大】">錠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">定</rdg></app>光</l>
<lb n="0681a25" ed="T"/><l>如恒沙等佛</l><l>我悉於中見</l>
<lb n="0681a26" ed="T"/><l>欲聞十方佛</l><l>所說悉覺識</l>
<lb n="0681a27" ed="T"/><l>當專習是經</l><l>一切可疾得</l>
<lb n="0681a28" ed="T"/><l>若願嚴佛國</l><l>合成弟子眾</l>
<lb n="0681a29" ed="T"/><l>光相及種好</l><l>當從是經得</l>
<pb n="0681b" xml:id="T19.1011.0681b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0681b01" ed="T"/><l>能除放<note n="0681009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">逸＝泆【宋】＊</note><app n="0681009"><lem wit="【大】">逸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">泆</rdg></app>念</l><l>七日專<note n="0681010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惟＝唯【三】＊</note><note n="0681010" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->惟＝唯【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0681010"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">唯</rdg></app>是</l>
<lb n="0681b02" ed="T"/><l>八十億佛臻</l><l>共授以此持</l>
<lb n="0681b03" ed="T"/><l>不以意思意</l><l>亦不思無意</l>
<lb n="0681b04" ed="T"/><l>意而不有思</l><l>然後可得持</l>
<lb n="0681b05" ed="T"/><l>宜熟解此經</l><l><note n="0681011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">勿＝物【宋】</note><app n="0681011"><lem wit="【大】">勿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">物</rdg></app>有<note n="0681012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">忘＝望【三】</note><note n="0681012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忘＝望【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681012"><lem wit="【大】">忘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">望</rdg></app>於道</l>
<lb n="0681b06" ed="T"/><l>得此持如海</l><l>不復勤於財</l>
<lb n="0681b07" ed="T"/><l>欲安諸天人</l><l>一切願無難</l>
<lb n="0681b08" ed="T"/><l>此為道之<note n="0681013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">座＝生【元】【明】</note><app n="0681013"><lem wit="【大】">座</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">生</rdg></app></l><l>但當正意行</l></lg>
<lb n="0681b09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0681b0901">又舍利弗菩薩有四法行。疾得是持。何等為
<lb n="0681b10" ed="T"/>四。<note n="0681014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＝以【元】【明】</note><app n="0681014"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>厭惡於愛欲。<note n="0681015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">己＝以【三】</note><note n="0681015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">己＝以【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681015"><lem wit="【大】">己</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>無賊害於眾生。以一
<lb n="0681b11" ed="T"/>切有而為布施。以無疲厭晝夜樂法。復有四
<lb n="0681b12" ed="T"/>法行疾得是持。何等為四。能習山澤居內。行
<lb n="0681b13" ed="T"/>深法忍不慕彼利養。行無量施不惜軀命。復
<lb n="0681b14" ed="T"/>有四法行疾得是持。何等為四。一曰入八字
<lb n="0681b15" ed="T"/>義。八字義者謂迹敏惟棄悲調滅忍。<note n="0681016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">常書＝當盡【宋】，當書【元】【明】</note><note n="0681016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常書＝當盡【宋】，＝當書【元】【明】</note><app n="0681016"><lem wit="【大】">常書</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">當盡</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">當書</rdg></app>持
<lb n="0681b16" ed="T"/>是。二曰誦說常以調<note n="0681017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">意＝音【三】</note><note n="0681017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意＝音【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681017"><lem wit="【大】">意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">音</rdg></app>。三曰內性合是法
<lb n="0681b17" ed="T"/>要。四曰勸行大道之行。菩薩如此為疾得持。
<lb n="0681b18" ed="T"/>於是佛說偈<note n="0681018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">言＝曰【三】</note><note n="0681018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＝曰【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681018"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">曰</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0681b19" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0681b1901"><l>當棄欲苦行</l><l><note n="0681019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">速＝遠【三】</note><note n="0681019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">速＝遠【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681019"><lem wit="【大】">速</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">遠</rdg></app>捨愚癡地</l>
<lb n="0681b20" ed="T"/><l>無自恣作惡</l><l>惡令墮惡道</l>
<lb n="0681b21" ed="T"/><l>是不作彼近</l><l>不知利譽事</l>
<lb n="0681b22" ed="T"/><l>愛眼視眾人</l><l>必貴如得色</l>
<lb n="0681b23" ed="T"/><l>眾人之有諍</l><l>皆由貪為本</l>
<lb n="0681b24" ed="T"/><l>故盡汲汲劇</l><l>棄是乃得持</l>
<lb n="0681b25" ed="T"/><l>欲法者晝夜</l><l>捨異<anchor xml:id="fxT19p0681b01"/>唯道求</l>
<lb n="0681b26" ed="T"/><l>得持而心向</l><l>是以常見經</l>
<lb n="0681b27" ed="T"/><l>閑居習佛教</l><l>住此不知彼</l>
<lb n="0681b28" ed="T"/><l>深忍却放<app type="star" corresp="#0681009"><lem wit="【大】">逸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">泆</rdg></app></l><l>常如救頭然</l>
<lb n="0681b29" ed="T"/><l>法不<app type="star" corresp="#0680009"><lem wit="【大】">猗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">倚</rdg></app>知利</l><l>亦不有身求</l>
<pb n="0681c" xml:id="T19.1011.0681c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0681c01" ed="T"/><l>見失當棄利</l><l>人以利為行</l>
<lb n="0681c02" ed="T"/><l>快哉得佛教</l><l>捨家離眾苦</l>
<lb n="0681c03" ed="T"/><l>信者成道學</l><l>敬佛法為智</l>
<lb n="0681c04" ed="T"/><l>智士不貪利</l><l>何況行法者</l>
<lb n="0681c05" ed="T"/><l>佛從遠斯成</l><l>故當捨利求</l>
<lb n="0681c06" ed="T"/><l>當思八字義</l><l>善書持<note n="0681020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此＝是【三】</note><note n="0681020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此＝是【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681020"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">是</rdg></app>經</l>
<lb n="0681c07" ed="T"/><l>常誦用調已</l><l>亦以開化人</l>
<lb n="0681c08" ed="T"/><l>得坐大智<note n="0681021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">署＝者【宋】</note><app n="0681021"><lem wit="【大】">署</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">者</rdg></app></l><l>一切見十方</l>
<lb n="0681c09" ed="T"/><l>無量佛在前</l><l>勸成其道欲</l></lg>
<lb n="0681c10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0681c1001">又舍利弗菩薩有四德為是持。何等為四。一
<lb n="0681c11" ed="T"/>曰常念諸佛。二曰不有邪行。三曰疾除行蓋。
<lb n="0681c12" ed="T"/>四曰得入無量門微密之持。有昔舍利弗往
<lb n="0681c13" ed="T"/>無央<note n="0681022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">數＋（劫）【三】</note><note n="0681022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">數＋（劫）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681022"><lem wit="【大】">數</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">數劫</rdg></app>不可計劫。時有佛名寶首曜王號如
<lb n="0681c14" ed="T"/>來至真等正覺明行成為善逝世間解無上士
<lb n="0681c15" ed="T"/>道法御天人師為佛眾祐。度人無量臨滅度
<lb n="0681c16" ed="T"/>時。世有轉輪王名光秉。其太子曰無念德首。
<lb n="0681c17" ed="T"/>年千<note n="0681023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">八＝六【三】</note><note n="0681023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八＝六【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681023"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">六</rdg></app>百歲。從佛<note n="0681024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">得聞＝聞得【三】</note><note n="0681024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得聞＝聞得【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681024"><lem wit="【大】">得聞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">聞得</rdg></app>此持而即奉行。又
<lb n="0681c18" ed="T"/>七千歲未曾睡臥。又七千歲未曾起身愛。又
<lb n="0681c19" ed="T"/>七千歲未曾念財利。又七千歲一心念行未
<lb n="0681c20" ed="T"/>曾傾倚於是則見九十億佛悉聞說法皆從受
<lb n="0681c21" ed="T"/>持。便作沙門積九萬歲。以是無量門微密之
<lb n="0681c22" ed="T"/>持。解說眾人於一世中。成就八十億人。使行
<lb n="0681c23" ed="T"/>無上正真之道。誘進<note n="0681025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔令〕－【三】</note><note n="0681025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔令〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0681025"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>出家立不退轉地。彼
<lb n="0681c24" ed="T"/>時眾中有尊者子名為月行。聞是法要盡心
<lb n="0681c25" ed="T"/>願樂。以此德本值七十億佛。皆從得上持逮
<lb n="0681c26" ed="T"/>諸菩薩無量之辯。其後三劫悉見諸佛。三劫
<lb n="0681c27" ed="T"/>末時月行得佛名曰錠光。號如來至真等正
<lb n="0681c28" ed="T"/>覺明行成為善逝世間解無上士道法御天人
<lb n="0681c29" ed="T"/>師為佛眾祐。又彼太子無念德首。講說法者
<pb n="0682a" xml:id="T19.1011.0682a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0682a01" ed="T"/>則今西方無量壽佛是<note n="0682001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔也〕－【三】</note><note n="0682001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔也〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682001"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。此賢劫中諸菩薩
<lb n="0682a02" ed="T"/>聞是法願樂者。皆得除後四十萬劫生死之
<lb n="0682a03" ed="T"/>行。又是學者欲疾作佛。若<note n="0682002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（後）＋得【三】</note><note n="0682002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（後）＋得【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682002"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">後得</rdg></app>是經如有願樂
<lb n="0682a04" ed="T"/>道行之意。則是當立不退轉地。必為無上正
<lb n="0682a05" ed="T"/>真之道。何況書持誦行。一切人民莫能稱量
<lb n="0682a06" ed="T"/>說其福也。於是佛說偈<note n="0682003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">曰＝言【三】</note><note n="0682003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曰＝言【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682003"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">言</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0682a07" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0682a0701"><l>常<note n="0682004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">修＝惟【三】</note><note n="0682004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">修＝惟【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682004"><lem wit="【大】">修</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惟</rdg></app>念佛者</l><l>眾邪不得便</l>
<lb n="0682a08" ed="T"/><l>行蓋<note n="0682005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">用＝欲【三】</note><note n="0682005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">用＝欲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682005"><lem wit="【大】">用</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">欲</rdg></app>疾除</l><l>得妙無量持</l>
<lb n="0682a09" ed="T"/><l>聞經心願樂</l><l>書持敬諷誦</l>
<lb n="0682a10" ed="T"/><l>天人莫能計</l><l>福廣無有量</l>
<lb n="0682a11" ed="T"/><l>所生輒見佛</l><l>信向不迴動</l>
<lb n="0682a12" ed="T"/><l>體解深經要</l><l>疾覺<note n="0682006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">斯＝無【三】</note><note n="0682006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斯＝無【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682006"><lem wit="【大】">斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">無</rdg></app>上道</l>
<lb n="0682a13" ed="T"/><l>得持惡道斷</l><l>不失定大財</l>
<lb n="0682a14" ed="T"/><l>色好常見佛</l><l>即至<note n="0682007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">覺＝無【三】</note><note n="0682007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">覺＝無【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682007"><lem wit="【大】">覺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">無</rdg></app>上道</l>
<lb n="0682a15" ed="T"/><l>尊者子聞持</l><l>即追識宿命</l>
<lb n="0682a16" ed="T"/><l>見佛九十億</l><l>得道如其願</l>
<lb n="0682a17" ed="T"/><l>若欲疾成佛</l><l>道力降<note n="0682008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">眾＝諸【三】</note><note n="0682008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眾＝諸【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682008"><lem wit="【大】">眾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">諸</rdg></app>魔</l>
<lb n="0682a18" ed="T"/><l>欲滿百福相</l><l>行此非有難</l>
<lb n="0682a19" ed="T"/><l>如滿<note n="0682009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">恒＝江【三】</note><note n="0682009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恒＝江【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682009"><lem wit="【大】">恒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">江</rdg></app>沙剎</l><l>積寶以布施</l>
<lb n="0682a20" ed="T"/><l>比書持此福</l><l>終不得為比</l></lg>
<lb n="0682a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0682a2101">是舍利弗菩薩行持者。有八大神在雪山中。
<lb n="0682a22" ed="T"/>共視護之。其名曰勇決神果強神。饒裕神雄
<lb n="0682a23" ed="T"/>猛神。體行神清<note n="0682010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">潔＝淨【三】</note><note n="0682010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">潔＝淨【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682010"><lem wit="【大】">潔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">淨</rdg></app>神。難勝神多安神。斯神
<lb n="0682a24" ed="T"/>必<note n="0682011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">來＋（下）【三】</note><note n="0682011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來＋（下）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682011"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">來下</rdg></app>。常當澡浴淨其被服正色經行。慈念眾
<lb n="0682a25" ed="T"/>生思是<note n="0682012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＝經【三】</note><note n="0682012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法＝經【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682012"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">經</rdg></app>要。神面不遠必安定誦。復有八菩
<lb n="0682a26" ed="T"/>薩今在欲行天。常當存念。其<note n="0682013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">名＋（曰）【三】</note><note n="0682013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">名＋（曰）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682013"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">名曰</rdg></app>無愛天<note n="0682014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（無）＋悅【三】</note><note n="0682014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（無）＋悅【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682014"><lem wit="【大】">悅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">無悅</rdg></app>
<lb n="0682a27" ed="T"/>可天。智光天懷金天。積習天願滿天。星王天
<lb n="0682a28" ed="T"/>行審天。斯皆敏行此持<note n="0682015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">者＋（也）【三】</note><note n="0682015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者＋（也）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682015"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">者也</rdg></app>。當諦惟持而常恭
<lb n="0682a29" ed="T"/>敬。<note n="0682016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＝以【三】</note><note n="0682016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已＝以【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682016"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>如應行微妙法忍。<note n="0682017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無＝不【三】</note><note n="0682017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無＝不【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682017"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">不</rdg></app>得<note n="0682018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（輙）＋輕【三】</note><note n="0682018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（輙）＋輕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682018"><lem wit="【大】">輕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">輙輕</rdg></app>試。說<note n="0682019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔是法〕－【三】</note><note n="0682019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是法〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682019"><lem wit="【大】">是
<pb n="0682b" xml:id="T19.1011.0682b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0682b01" ed="T"/>法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>時恒沙等菩薩。皆得是持而不退轉。六十
<lb n="0682b02" ed="T"/>姟天與人未發道意<note n="0682020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔者〕－【三】</note><note n="0682020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682020"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。今皆發<note n="0682021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔起〕－【三】</note><note n="0682021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔起〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682021"><lem wit="【大】">起</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>無上正真
<lb n="0682b03" ed="T"/>之道。賢者舍利弗白佛言。<note n="0682022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">當＝以【三】</note><note n="0682022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當＝以【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0682022"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>何名此經。佛言
<lb n="0682b04" ed="T"/>是法之要。名無量門微密之持。一名成道降
<lb n="0682b05" ed="T"/>魔得一切智。當奉持之。佛說是已皆歡喜受。</p>
<lb n="0682b06" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛說無量門微密持經</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
